General code structure:
1. ⁠Employee menu: includes options to view users and exit.
2. Main menu: includes options for user login, employee login, user registration and logout.
3. Functions: functions like login_user(), login_employee(), register_user() and view_users() to manage various operations.
Performance process:
•⁠ ⁠The program runs in an endless loop until the user decides to exit.
By choosing each option, the corresponding function will be called to perform the desired operation.
